{"id": "ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 92, "displayName": {"text": "Kith Beverly Hills", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CVE1YaDJUall5YlRadGRHOWtlR1pSUmtZdFRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "This was my first time visiting the Kith on Rodeo Drive. The store itself was very clean and beautifully maintained.\n\nWhen I asked to try on a pair of Converse shoes, it took more than 10 minutes for the staff to bring them. I eventually had to ask them to hurry before they brought the shoes out.\n\nI am Asian, and the staff member assisting me was a Black woman with cornrows. During the interaction, I felt uncomfortable and sensed that I was being treated differently. The overall attitude did not feel welcoming or attentive.\n\nI also visited the Malibu location, where the service was excellent and the staff were very kind. Unfortunately, my experience at the Rodeo Drive store was very disappointing, and I do not plan to return.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This was my first time visiting the Kith on Rodeo Drive. The store itself was very clean and beautifully maintained.\n\nWhen I asked to try on a pair of Converse shoes, it took more than 10 minutes for the staff to bring them. I eventually had to ask them to hurry before they brought the shoes out.\n\nI am Asian, and the staff member assisting me was a Black woman with cornrows. During the interaction, I felt uncomfortable and sensed that I was being treated differently. The overall attitude did not feel welcoming or attentive.\n\nI also visited the Malibu location, where the service was excellent and the staff were very kind. Unfortunately, my experience at the Rodeo Drive store was very disappointing, and I do not plan to return.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "hiro", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113926335721037035919/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmz3x0S051WP_OQAVIJGVEy_QEXY1CWxMw3Y3NsHmA-Bng=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-22T06:20:29.742866496Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CVE1YaDJUall5YlRadGRHOWtlR1pSUmtZdFRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CVE1YaDJUall5YlRadGRHOWtlR1pSUmtZdFRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb5657a2edd9:0x3ff15a4de39e1ab1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JMFJXUXdkbEY2WkRoYVdtMTRVMVpNTW1KM1RXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "When it comes to Kith, we’re blessed to have multiple stores to choose from (Kith Malibu, Sunset and Rodeo) but the crew at Rodeo always make me come back to this location. The store feels like home, with every person there always wanting to support, showcase new pieces and always taking care of you from when you walk in to when you walk out.\n\nAs a kith fan, I’ll go in for just ice cream and end up walking out learning something about the new collection, the material and background of new items that just came in… you can never go wrong hitting the rodeo store and they’ll always have a customer for life in me.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "When it comes to Kith, we’re blessed to have multiple stores to choose from (Kith Malibu, Sunset and Rodeo) but the crew at Rodeo always make me come back to this location. The store feels like home, with every person there always wanting to support, showcase new pieces and always taking care of you from when you walk in to when you walk out.\n\nAs a kith fan, I’ll go in for just ice cream and end up walking out learning something about the new collection, the material and background of new items that just came in… you can never go wrong hitting the rodeo store and they’ll always have a customer for life in me.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jermean Tabar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117894695053192135978/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB4T-RA9zgkAyFbhshrDtGH2sYIQUbRowwbO1DnTHuBQzUkUU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-21T21:48:12.562022217Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JMFJXUXdkbEY2WkRoYVdtMTRVMVpNTW1KM1RXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JMFJXUXdkbEY2WkRoYVdtMTRVMVpNTW1KM1RXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb5657a2edd9:0x3ff15a4de39e1ab1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSbGRuWkpOamcyYWs1VFdreFhkVTVwZDNCSk0xRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The staff here are super friendly and made my whole experience pretty awesome.  I’ve heard that the stock generally runs lower than other locations in SoCal, but that wasn’t the case as I was able to grab a few regional exclusive that I wasn’t able to find at the WeHo location.  If you’re in Beverly Hills be sure to make a stop here for a fun and memorable experience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The staff here are super friendly and made my whole experience pretty awesome.  I’ve heard that the stock generally runs lower than other locations in SoCal, but that wasn’t the case as I was able to grab a few regional exclusive that I wasn’t able to find at the WeHo location.  If you’re in Beverly Hills be sure to make a stop here for a fun and memorable experience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tim Lam", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103465868918428571683/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYQBIMZrZBt-qHNJPApJhBPkkG5neQed_2cl5tRp9TokrrKS576w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-10T04:31:37.518313981Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSbGRuWkpOamcyYWs1VFdreFhkVTVwZDNCSk0xRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSbGRuWkpOamcyYWs1VFdreFhkVTVwZDNCSk0xRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb5657a2edd9:0x3ff15a4de39e1ab1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbk0zRnNTV3d3V0hveU5rNVNVbEY0ZDJablRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Heard that the service standard in the Tokyo one was quite bad, so I was truly pleasantly surprised with the Beverly Hills outlet!\n\nI am Asian visiting from overseas. And not once in my 90minutes in the store did I feel like I was treated differently.\n\nRather, Kith staff were excellent. Checking in with me every 5-10mins if I needed assistance. And they were more than happy to let me try on several pieces in various sizes was unsure about.\n\nReally enjoyed my experience there & spent about $700 as a result!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Heard that the service standard in the Tokyo one was quite bad, so I was truly pleasantly surprised with the Beverly Hills outlet!\n\nI am Asian visiting from overseas. And not once in my 90minutes in the store did I feel like I was treated differently.\n\nRather, Kith staff were excellent. Checking in with me every 5-10mins if I needed assistance. And they were more than happy to let me try on several pieces in various sizes was unsure about.\n\nReally enjoyed my experience there & spent about $700 as a result!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alvin Sim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100023617124142546558/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqn3ESxyp8QflUy4bjYEBzuz9C8ILUProD1jWTa3LGj5r1BhQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-06T04:17:56.861421438Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbk0zRnNTV3d3V0hveU5rNVNVbEY0ZDJablRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbk0zRnNTV3d3V0hveU5rNVNVbEY0ZDJablRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb5657a2edd9:0x3ff15a4de39e1ab1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2e2iV1a7woARsRqe401a8T8/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNma1lTTVlBEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Pretty cool store, decent selection of apparel, accessories, etc. All the sales associates were great & helpful, definitely a more chill vibe than most stores on Rodeo Drive. Without doubt have to try the Kith Treats in the back of store, what a cool thing to have in a store, especially on Rodeo Drive!!\nI have to say…. definitely stop by and purchase something!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Pretty cool store, decent selection of apparel, accessories, etc. All the sales associates were great & helpful, definitely a more chill vibe than most stores on Rodeo Drive. Without doubt have to try the Kith Treats in the back of store, what a cool thing to have in a store, especially on Rodeo Drive!!\nI have to say…. definitely stop by and purchase something!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "J’s Life", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105331266537901117407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeLtFV3lYcUiO_PsKOQzxKzVcrCiUqP_uJFcT1YEgYov-0fWmq=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2024-12-29T22:56:49.150353Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNma1lTTVlBEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNma1lTTVlBEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2bb5657a2edd9:0x3ff